%h1 About
%p.indented
  This subdomain is where we will be housing all of our prototypes. Currently, we are using this web application as a way to experiment with various solutions to help cope with the changing media environment. Our original site can be found by going to #{link_to 'Capital Musings', 'http://www.capitalmusings.com'}.
%p.indented
  You can
  =link_to "sign up", new_user_registration_path
  to receive the briefing that we compile from outside sources on a daily basis. This is but one tool we use to stay on top of the endless barrage of news.

